data.description: Delight in this spacious 5-bedroom, 3.5-bath residence, featuring a finished basement complete with an additional bedroom and full bath. Perfectly situated near all your daily needs-mere minutes from grocery stores, popular restaurants, and direct freeway access. Families will appreciate the excellent Westfield schools in proximity. Enjoy outdoor moments in a generous backyard, perfect for gatherings and relaxation. Situated within a serene and friendly community, this home offers both convenience and tranquility. Don't miss out on this gem!
